<span class="line"><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">	</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">void</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;"> </span><span style="color:#61AFEF;">play</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">()</span><span style="color:#7F848E;font-style:italic;"> // 该方法继承于VGA,实现中调用hdmi的play，相当于就是转换头，做不同接口的信号转换的</span></span>
